name: Dr. Valeriya Itkina
about:
Dr. Valeriya Itkina is a compassionate and skilled dentist practicing at VisoDent NY in Manhattan. She specializes in addressing a wide range of dental concerns, including broken teeth, wisdom tooth issues, toothaches, and cavities. Dr. Itkina is dedicated to providing high-quality dental care.

At VisoDent NY, Dr. Itkina is part of a team of experienced and compassionate dental professionals dedicated to providing personalized attention and a gentle touch. The practice offers a range of services, including preventive care, restorative procedures, and cosmetic treatments, all aimed at helping patients achieve and maintain optimal oral health and radiant confidence.

questionResponses.response: Patients should choose VisoDent NY for their dental care because of our commitment to delivering high-quality, personalized care in a comfortable, sophisticated environment. Our practice combines cutting-edge technology with a compassionate and experienced team, ensuring that each visit is not only effective but also pleasant. Whether you're seeking a routine checkup, smile makeover, or restorative treatment, we tailor our services to meet your specific needs. At VisoDent NY, we value long-term relationships with our patients and prioritize preventive care to help maintain optimal oral health, making us a trusted partner for your dental journey.

question.question: Why should patients choose you as their provider instead of others in the area
question.example: I've been practicing dentistry for over 17 years, and treat a wide range of issues. Our practices focuses on making sure that you are 100% involved in your healthcare choices, and that you always feel safe and comfortable. Our practice also offers a wide range of payment options to match your needs.

questionResponses.response:
At VisoDent NY, the top three treatments we focus on are:

Dental Bonding - Ideal for repairing minor chips or cracks, dental bonding restores the appearance and strength of teeth with a quick, efficient procedure.

Fillings - We provide high-quality, tooth-colored fillings to restore function and appearance in cavities or fractured teeth, ensuring a durable and natural look.

Invisalign - For those seeking a discreet and comfortable way to straighten their teeth, we offer Invisalign, a clear aligner system that provides an effective solution for achieving a straighter smile.

question.question: What are the top 3 treatments that you focus on
question.example: I am skilled in all areas of dentistry, but primarily focus on Cosmetics, Invisalign, Oral Surgery and Teeth Whitening in my practice. I believe very strongly in continuing my education and completing advanced training programs in Orthodontics, Periodontics, Endodontics and Cosmetic Dentistry to make sure I can provide the highest quality of dentistry to all my patients.

questionResponses.response: At VisoDent NY, we are proud of our dedication to providing personalized, high-quality care in a comfortable and welcoming environment. Our advanced technologies and experienced team enable us to offer a wide range of treatments tailored to each patient’s unique needs. We take great pride in building strong relationships with our patients, ensuring they receive the best possible care while maintaining their oral health and confidence.

question.question: What are you proud of in your practice
question.example: Something that makes me very proud is that our practice has good reviews because of our experienced staff, attractive aesthetics and advanced equipment. It's fully accessible and designed for geriatric care and patients with mobility issues.

questionResponses.response: At VisoDent NY, we particularly enjoy treating cases that involve smile makeovers, dental repairs, and teeth straightening with Invisalign. We find it incredibly rewarding to help patients restore their smiles and confidence, whether through simple procedures like dental bonding to repair minor chips or more comprehensive treatments like transforming a crooked smile with Invisalign. These cases allow us to make a significant impact on our patients' well-being and self-esteem, helping them achieve a smile they can be proud of.

question.question: Which cases do you enjoy treating? Why
question.example: I truly enjoy treating all my patients. However, one of the most rewarding moments for a dentist is to see a patient leave the office with a beautiful smile on their face while only a short time ago they were experiencing discomfort, pain or embarrassment to smile.
